00:42:06,710 --> 00:42:07,610
Sure. Hurry up and finish it up.

805
00:42:07,690 --> 00:42:08,390
Okay.

806
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:11,510
Chu Li, I'll leave the library to you.

807
00:42:11,790 --> 00:42:12,670
Okay.

808
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:16,670
Great!

809
00:42:16,670 --> 00:42:18,590
Jiang Yu Cheng has finally come back!

810
00:42:18,590 --> 00:42:20,390
The day has finally come!

811
00:42:26,870 --> 00:42:28,990
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.

812
00:42:30,220 --> 00:42:31,130
Chu Li.

813
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:33,870
Do you know Mr Jiang Yu Cheng's
works very well?

814
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:34,520
Indeed.

815
00:42:34,620 --> 00:42:37,400
I've read each of his novels
more than five times.

816
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:41,150
Then can you help me to do
the PowerPoint presentation for him?

817
00:42:41,240 --> 00:42:43,560
Huh? I help you to do it?

818
00:42:43,640 --> 00:42:45,800
I've something important on tonight.

819
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:47,420
I really can't make it.

820
00:42:47,430 --> 00:42:48,920
Please.

821
00:42:49,930 --> 00:42:52,140
But if I help you to do it,

822
00:42:52,230 --> 00:42:55,130
how can you communicate with Mr Jiang

823
00:42:55,210 --> 00:42:57,100
without understanding the contents?

824
00:42:57,110 --> 00:42:58,190
Don't you worry.

825
00:42:58,200 --> 00:43:00,280
I'll memorise all the contents.

826
00:43:02,660 --> 00:43:03,950
Xiao Niao.

827
00:43:04,050 --> 00:43:06,950
Did you find Mr Jiang's Jiangnan Circuit

828
00:43:07,040 --> 00:43:08,280
a good read?

829
00:43:09,510 --> 00:43:11,260
I read it when I was in high school.

830
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:14,010
But it's been a long time.
I don't remember it well.

831
00:43:15,710 --> 00:43:18,590
Jiangnan Circuit is Mr Kou Wei's work.

832
00:43:20,160 --> 00:43:21,210
Xiao Niao.

833
00:43:21,300 --> 00:43:22,980
It's not that I'm not willing to help you.

834
00:43:23,060 --> 00:43:25,430
But since Miao asked
you to contact Mr Jiang,

835
00:43:25,520 --> 00:43:28,260
it's your job to understand his works.

836
00:43:28,340 --> 00:43:31,160
That's the way to
show respect for the author.

837
00:43:31,730 --> 00:43:33,020
I'm really sorry.

838
00:43:33,090 --> 00:43:35,780
I can't help you with it.

839
00:44:10,460 --> 00:44:20,840
[Little Monkey]

840
00:44:11,110 --> 00:44:12,100
[Mr Zhou Chuan.]

841
00:44:12,210 --> 00:44:14,540
[Can I come to your place this afternoon?]

842
00:44:14,720 --> 00:44:17,880
Fine. You just want to
see me for the seal, don't you?

843
00:44:26,170 --> 00:44:30,920
[Chu Li]
[Zhou Chuan]

844
00:44:27,830 --> 00:44:30,540
[The seal. Come here at once.]
